{:synth/id   :granular-voice
 :synth/tags [:sample :granular :bus-aware]
 :synth/doc  "TGrains-based granular synthesis voice. Reads from a loaded SC buffer.
Set :buf to the SC buffer ID. :pos is normalised position 0–1 through the buffer.
:density controls grain trigger rate (grains/sec). :dur is grain duration in seconds.
:rate is grain playback rate (pitch). Writes to :out-bus for use in patches.

Use with the :granular-cloud patch:
  (def inst (sc/instantiate-patch! :granular-cloud))
  (sc/set-patch-param! inst :buf my-buffer-id)
  (sc/set-patch-param! inst :density 12)"
 :args  {:buf         0
         :density     8
         :pos         0.5
         :pos-spread  0.05
         :rate        1.0
         :dur         0.12
         :pan         0.0
         :amp         0.6
         :out-bus     8}
 :graph [:out :out-bus
          [:t-grains 2
           [:dust :density]
           :buf
           :rate
           [:* :pos [:buf-frames :buf]]
           :dur
           :pan
           :amp
           3]]}
